  "summary": {
    "zh": "F1 方向盘既是转向器，又是车手的控制中枢与数据仪表盘：换档拨片、离合器拨片、快拆机构与中央 LCD 显示屏把整辆赛车的调校与信息集中到指尖。",
    "en": "An F1 steering wheel is simultaneously a steerer, control hub and data display: shift paddles, clutch paddles, quick-release and a central LCD put the whole car's setup and readouts at the driver's fingertips."
  },
